{"tid":1876526,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔益你吹咩] 政府撥逾228萬予兩機構賑濟菲律賓風災災民","createTime":"2020-02-12T12:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T12:33:25.000Z","uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"39f7c7478eef0386a7cf10c564ef2297b57448d2","tid":1876526,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:33:25.000Z","msg":"2020-02-12 HKT 19:12<br />\n<br />\n特區政府撥款228萬多元予兩間機構，賑濟菲律賓風災的災民。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，接納賑災基金諮詢委員建議，分別批出逾76萬及152萬元予<span style=\"color: red;\">安澤中國（香港）救援協會</span>及<span style=\"color: red;\">樂施會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n撥款會用於提供家庭和衛生用品，以及臨時居所物料，約2萬4500名災民受惠，兩間救援機構將會進行賑災的地點並不相同，並沒有資源重疊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508184-20200212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508184-20200212.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GPLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=677b4c30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508184-20200212.htm&h=6306ba9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508184-20200212.htm</a>"}]}